c: 3
v: 36
t: "Then when she delivered her [child Maryam (Mary)], she said: \"O my Lord! I have delivered a female child,\" - and Allah knew better what she delivered, - \"And the male is not like the female, and I have named her Maryam (Mary), and I seek refuge with You (Allah) for her and for her offspring from Shaitan (Satan), the outcast"